cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper deals with the problem of registration of two point cloud scans using deep learning techniques. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also introduces a novel approach using auto-encoders and relative pose estimation networks, which involves machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper also discusses a hypothesize-and-verify algorithm, which falls under the domain of graphics (cs.GR).
